ing incident.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/17-killed-as-speeding-minibus-crashes-into-parked-bus-in-pakistans-khyber-pakhtunkhwa/articleshow/131312087.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/17-killed-as-speeding-minibus-crashes-into-parked-bus-in-pakistans-khyber-pakhtunkhwa/articleshow/131312087.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-25T20:23:14+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131312154,imgsize-829999.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[3 new visa pilots in US Consulate in Kolkata: 'Shorter wait times for those who....']]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131311910.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/3-new-visa-pilots-in-us-consulate-in-kolkata-shorter-wait-times-for-those-who-/articleshow/131311910.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/3-new-visa-pilots-in-us-consulate-in-kolkata-shorter-wait-times-for-those-who-/articleshow/131311910.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-25T20:11:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131311951,imgsize-150118.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Ebola scare: Congo hospitals attacked, infected patients escape]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131311510.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/attacks-on-congo-health-facilities-trigger-escape-of-ebola-patients-hamper-response-efforts/articleshow/131311510.cms]]></li